{"tid":2304554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長期戴口罩其實有冇身體問題？","createTime":"2020-11-29T02:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T04:43:32.000Z","uid":338879,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ee75694a749452e14c257112c1b40b10f7122f63","tid":2304554,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"影響呼吸同聚菌？<br />\n有冇醫學撚講下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細胞缺氧的身體，百病叢生<br />\n<br />\n人必須有足夠的空氣、空氣的重要性在於它含有氧氣，缺氧發生在腦部時，就會讓人想昏睡，產生頭腦混沌不清且昏昏沉沉，而身體細胞長期缺乏足夠氧氣就不能正常地生產能量及運作，因而容易衰老、生病。德國生化學家華寶博士（Dr. Otto Warburg）<strong><span class=\"gold\">就在1923年證明癌症是由細胞的缺氧所引起。造成身體缺氧的可能性很多，例如長期配戴不合適口罩、</span></strong>精神壓力過大及缺少運動等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n汁：支01<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/471921/%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BB%A4%E7%B4%B0%E8%83%9E%E7%BC%BA%E6%B0%A7-%E5%B0%8D%E4%BA%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%B7%B1%E9%81%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%2F471921%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E8%2583%259E%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A7-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E9%2581%25A0&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ed6432e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/471921/%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BB%A4%E7%B4%B0%E8%83%9E%E7%BC%BA%E6%B0%A7-%E5%B0%8D%E4%BA%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%B7%B1%E9%81%A0</a>"},{"pid":"fa0b5901b1a78d392161612a4fe18b95eaace92d","tid":2304554,"uid":112845,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa422c5db572193f7b5d28e693789927e68aee2","tid":2304554,"uid":338879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa0b5901b1a78d392161612a4fe1